documentation.text:
FLASH LOAN ARBITRAGE CONTRACT
 
 
 Este contrato ejecuta arbitraje atmico usando Flash Loans de Aave V3.
 Soporta mltiples DEXs: Uniswap V3, SushiSwap, Curve
 
 Caractersticas:
 - Flash Loans sin colateral de Aave V3
 - Arbitraje multi-DEX atmico
 - MEV Protection (deadline, slippage)
 - Profit validation antes de ejecutar
@notice Aave callback - execute arbitrage with borrowed funds

 - Simulacin on-chain antes de ejecutar
 - MEV Protection con deadline y slippage
 - Profit validation
